rows.label: qev050302_MSG0001
rows.name:
Why is my Skell picking up...?
Vi Sezha! Is that you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0002
rows.name: How many times did I tell you not to come?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0003
rows.name: This is my fight. I shall not involve you in it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_JNK0010
rows.name: Join

rows.label: qev050302_SEL0011
rows.name: Say that you have come to assist her.

rows.label: qev050302_JNK0020
rows.name: Explain

rows.label: qev050302_SEL0021
rows.name: Tell Ge Jewhe that Vi Sezha sent you to help.

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0004
rows.name:
This is my people's grudge, human.
I will not drag an outsider into it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0005
rows.name: ...What? Vi Sezha sent you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0006
rows.name:
Rrrgh! I told her to forget about me for her own good!
But she never did listen.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0007
rows.name: ...Vi Sezha sent you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0008
rows.name:
Rrrgh! I told her to forget about me for her own good!
But she never did listen.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0009
rows.name:
I saw too many good men and women die needlessly
as pawns of the Ganglion. I will drink a toast to them
with the blood of our enemies.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0010
rows.name:
I am sorry for your trouble. Please return to Vi Sezha
and tell her that Ge Jewhe has perished in glory.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_JNK0030
rows.name: Lecture

rows.label: qev050302_SEL0031
rows.name: Demand that Ge Jewhe consider Vi Sezha's feelings.

rows.label: qev050302_JNK0040
rows.name: Convince

rows.label: qev050302_SEL0041
rows.name: Persuade Ge Jewhe with logic.

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0011
rows.name:
I have spent far longer considering her than you know,
human.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0012
rows.name:
But I cannot live with the knowledge that the Ganglion's
insults to my people remain unanswered![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0013
rows.name:
You speak in proofs and details. All I know is that
there exists something more important than my life,
or even the bonds I share with others.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0014
rows.name: The insults to my people must be answered for![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0015
rows.name:
I am a warrior before I am a woman.
Even if it means breaking Vi Sezha's heart,
I walk the path of vengeance.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0016
rows.name:
...I should cast away this bracelet now.
Take my own advice and forget about her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0017
rows.name:
A woman about to die has no use for sentiment.
I wish to leave regrets behind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050302_MSG0018
rows.name:
You should leave this dangerous place.
It is crawling with Marnuck scouts.[ST:wait ]
